summary: An ordinance providing for the acquisition by condemnation of certain property between Alki Avenue and Sunset Avenue, in the general vicinity of West Massachusetts Street, and described as a portion of an unnumbered tract, as shown on the plat of West Seattle Park Addition (portion of Government Lot 3, Section 11, Township 24 North, Range 3 East, W. M.), for slide protection purposes.
committee: Parks and Public Grounds and Finance
